branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
VQ valves are ideal for applications requiring high speed, frequent operation, stable response time and long service life. Innovative mounting methods allow valves to be changed without entirely disassembling the manifold. Built-in one-touch fittings save piping time and labor.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Base mounted, plug-in type manifold for VQ2*0* valve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;D-sub connector (25 pin standard, 15 pin option)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Top or side receptacle position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maximum 24 stations available as standard&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12 port sizes available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optional DIN rail mount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

